\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Recruiter Self\uc0\u8209 Service Appointment Scheduler\
\
A lightweight Flask web application that allows recruiters to publish their availability and let candidates self\uc0\u8209 schedule interview slots. The system prevents double bookings, stores all appointments in simple JSON files, and allows candidates to reschedule once with a mandatory reason. This prototype demonstrates how a small automation can streamline recruitment workflows without requiring external calendar integrations.\
\
---\
\
##  Features\
\
- Recruiter can add available interview slots  \
- Candidates can book any available slot  \
- Automatic prevention of double bookings  \
- Candidates may reschedule **once only**, with a required reason  \
- All data stored in `availability.json` and `appointments.json`  \
- Simple HTML templates for a clean, minimal interface  \
- Built using **Flask**, **Python**, and **JSON storage**\
\
